Author: teahappy
Text: i’m sorry, OP. i’m struggling to recover from an intense b/p circle as well and i know how you feel.    i always feel dirty and sick afterwards, and my throat hurts constantly   you can make it through this! i know that it may sound hypocritical coming from me, but it you have the strength to end this
